What is Numrology: 
Numrology is the ancient study of numbers. Each letter of the alphabets has a numeric value and all relationships can be defined in terms of numbers. Which further when combined with date of birth and name gives an insight into ones personality, strength, charater, and weakness, etc. When relationship is balanced and positive it resultes into growth and happiness. Whereas if the relationship is having imballanced numbers, the development counl not be seen there and a lot of passiveness could be felt. Always there be issues with such persons wchich will make them mentally disturbed. thus by doing a correct numeric reading such imbalances can be removed by adjusting the name in such a way that it brings happiness, positivity, growth, and prosperity, which is making numrology a powerful tool. 

